title: Pholicious
typeOfFood: Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Food counter in the mall offering a Vietnamese pho (rice noodle soup) that you can customize to be vegan. Choose the vegetable broth, a medley of vegetables, then add your choice of toppings like cilantro and mint leaves plus sauces (sirachi, sweet and sour, hoisin). Franchise concept with multiple locations.
